title: JOB FAIR at Skyline Place Senior Living! Friday, 10/16/15
text:
JOB FAIR at Skyline Place Senior Living! Friday, 10/16/15 ad date: 10/13/2015 
JOB FAIR at Skyline Place Senior Living! Friday, 10/16/15 10:00AM to 12:00PM. Interested in a job at Skyline Place Senior Living or Oak Terrace Memory Care? Come to our Job Fair prepared to complete an application and you will be interviewed on the spot! Candidates must pass a pre-employment background check and drug screen. E.O.E.
